HEADWORD: Administratrix
<hw>Ad*min`is*tra"trix</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL.]</ety> <def>A woman who administers; esp., one who administers
the estate of an intestate, or to whom letters of administration have
been granted; a female administrator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Admirability</ent>⟦br⟧
